parameters:
Tch! Who the hell are you guys! ...Huh? Two girls? What? Do
you think you came here to rescue her?

Hahaha... This is great!!! If I sell all three of them, I
can live a life of leisure for a while!

Hahaha! You dare to talk back, huh? Fine... I don't mind
feisty women. I'll keep you as my slave!

\SE[32] (Can I create an opening... Laura, can you cover for
me?)
ルナロア右へ、ラウラは左で挟み撃ちな形に

...What? Are you really planning to steal her from me?
...Hahaha! This is interesting!
ここで勇者ライアンくん下から登場

\SE[14] Ah, you scoundrel!! I, the hero Ryan, will be your
opponent!!
ルナロア右からタックル。
飛ばされたレベッカをラウラが受け止める
\SE[16]Shall we clean up... Are you prepared?
Damn it!! You think I'll let you have it your way!!

\SM[jump]\SE[14]Oh, I will fight too! You scoundrel!!
Prepare to face the blade of justice!!
ライアン参戦で戦闘開始。
大仰な技名が色々ある。まぁ弱いめで。
N-No, Ryan...! It's dangerous, so please hide.

Please, Lunaroa. Let me fight with you...? I will protect
Ryan...!
I can't refuse if you make that kind of face...
...I understand. Please be careful. I believe in you, Laura.
人さらいは端っこでのびてる。
レベッカは意識を取り戻してる。
Thank you, Ryan... You saved me.

N-No, I was completely reliant on Laura and the others... I
didn't do anything significant at all...
That's not true! Ryan, you were amazing, right?

That's right. I don't know what would have happened if there
hadn't been any help.

Ryan... I was so happy. Thank you for coming to help me...
You really were like a hero...
レベッカ、ライアンの目の前に接近

When we get back... I'll give you lots and lots... of
rewards ♡ Will that be okay... ♡?
ラウラたちに視線移動
Oh my, kids these days are quite advanced...

Is that so? Didn't Laura propose to me when we were around
that age?

Huh...!? No... um... That was definitely just a moment of
being carried away... or rather, you could say it was
youthful indiscretion...
Was it all just a game to you... with me?

...Hawaa!! No, that's not it! I mean, even when I'm serious,
I'm serious!! Um...!
You are always my number one...!

Oh my... I've been told something nice. I understand. I just
couldn't help but want to see Laura being all flustered...

I'm sorry? ...But Laura, your movements earlier were really
good, you know? Rebecca-chan didn't get hurt, and Ryan-kun
too...

Lunaroa is just amazing... I-I'm nothing special... I'm
small and insignificant...!

Don't belittle yourself. It's okay. You're gradually
becoming stronger.

It's me, who's been watching you all this time, saying it.
Don't worry. There's no mistake.

Besides... since I'm praising you, you should just be happy
about it... understood?
ルナロア。ラウラのそばに

When you come back, I'll give you lots and lots... of
rewards...♡, okay?
ルナロアドットで、ふきだしかなにかで…笑える？

I-I'm sorry... I couldn't help it because I was looking at
you with so much envy...
Uuu... My pure maiden's heart... is being toyed with...
Shall we go soon? We need to return those girls safely too.
ルナロア下へ。画面から消える・
C-Can I really receive the rewards as promised...!?
ラウラ追うようにダッシュ。で終わり。
編成にレベッカも追加。
強くはないけど、ライアンよりは一回り強い

There are a lot of customers today.... Oh, if you're done
with your business here, please talk to me and I'll escort
you to the entrance.

There's a Unique Boss on the lower floor... Hmm... What
should we do about this...

It might be a bit of a spoiler, but... Do you still want to
hear it?
I still want to hear it

Ehh... Am I really going to tell you...? Well, I guess I
have no choice...

If the Unique Boss is too strong, maybe you should defeat
the Story Boss first. It might be a good idea to take them
on in order. But please don't ask me why.
That's right. Let's pretend you didn't hear anything.
Good work~. Does it feel like you've finished a job...?
I want to go back to the entrance
Warp to the entrance of the mine?

It's fun to have more people! Numbers are power! We'll beat
up those Unique Monsters too!
\i[414] I obtained the horn of an angel! $
